categories: Category:Imperial Navy admirals of the Galactic Empire

nodes.text: Dalken Hol was an admiral in the Imperial Navy. Some time after the Battle of Yavin, Dalken was captured on Carida by Bossk and turned over to the Zann Consortium.
Bossk managed to defeat the academy's notable defense corps, which included a unit of Lancet Aerial Artillery, and the possible destruction of a set of barracks and a vehicle factory.
